text: Mielnik is a village and municipal seat in Podlaskie Voivodeship, north-east Poland. Mielnik may also refer to the following places: *Mielnik, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Mielnik, Subcarpathian Voivodeship (south-east Poland) *Mielnik, West Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-west Poland) *Gail McIntyre, Character in Coronation Street
title: Mielnik (disambiguation)
